2. 

In these Regulations— 

“Act of 1968” means Road Traffic Act 1968 (No. 25 of 1968); 

“Principal Act” means Road Traffic Act 1961 (No. 24 of 1961); 

“Regulations of 1975” means European Communities (Road Traffic) 
(Compulsory Insurance) Regulations 1975 (S.I. No. 178 of 1975); 

“Regulations of 1992” means European Communities (Road Traffic) 
(Compulsory Insurance) (Amendment) Regulations 1992 (S.I. No. 347 of 
1992); 

“Regulations of 2008” means European Communities (Motor Insurance) 
Regulations 2008 (S.I. No. 248 of 2008). 

